Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯？ 心愛你那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.50,0:00:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沾了好多污漬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哎呀呀 這是有努力工作的證明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是想要嚐嚐看給紗路的那杯熱可可做得怎麼樣來著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.87,0:00:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}會好好洗乾淨的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.73,0:00:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}看起來馬上就可以乾了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.86,0:00:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是個晴朗明媚的好天氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那真是困擾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.78,0:00:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:00:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}實際上洗衣機壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:01:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}修理人員似乎要明天才可以過來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要洗衣服的話 得去自助洗衣店
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦 心愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.37,0:01:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}來吧 一起去洗衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}用手洗嗎？！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}<OP>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個 心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃和理世也把衣服換下來啊 我也幫你們一起洗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}理世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你這麼用力的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}布料會洗壞的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}紗路？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真是的 看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}洗衣服應該是這樣做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不是用力了就可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}像這樣把弄髒的部分朝向裡面 用雙手像這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真不愧是紗路 我也來試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}像這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}再小點力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.58,0:03:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}有紗路指導就可以安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}紗路對手洗衣服已經很熟練了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}感覺被表揚了也高興不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛 你不覺得洗衣粉放得太多了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦？ 但是要想洗乾淨的就應該多放才對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:04:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}應該適量的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哇 有那麼多肥皂泡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不要讓它起泡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好厲害啊 有這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}誰可以吹出更多的肥皂泡 來一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我可不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}洗衣服呢？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}也請告訴我肥皂泡的製作方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}連智乃也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我換好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}肥皂泡…你們不是在洗衣服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}雖然很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我寶貴的肥皂泡 真是虛幻縹緲的東西啊 我的人生也是 一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}千夜！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這真的有在洗衣服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}學 學姐 那 那件制服我來幫你洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}當然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真是熟練啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不要用力過猛把理世的制服給弄破了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那樣的失敗怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}腋下那裡破掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}難道是我用力過猛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 那裡 昨天有勾到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這樣的話會被送上軍事法庭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}冷靜點 你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒關係的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊啊啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}怎麼了 智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}救 救命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我一點都不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}請別吃我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}快點成佛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:40.04,Default,,500,0,0,,{\be3}救救我 放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:40.74,Default,,0,400,0,,{\be3\}喂 快放開智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦 大家怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}窗簾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我是想把窗簾也一起洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}可是太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真是的 別嚇我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嘻嘻 抱歉啊 智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這些窗簾都得洗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這量也太多了點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我來讓你見識見識手洗的潛力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.62,0:07:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你那自信是從哪裡來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}來吧 開幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}洗衣服 洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}洗衣服 洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}洗 洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}洗 洗 洗衣服 洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}洗衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃很輕的 完全沒感覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}使勁踩過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我才不會再踩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}都已經洗了一小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}完 完全洗不完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒完沒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}人力還是贏不過機械嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不能就這麼放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}只要我們同心協力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就一定能獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}千夜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}請把力量借給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}早借你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你還是把腳動起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這是甘兔庵特製的綠茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}喝茶喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這顏色真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}裡面有一杯被我摻了青汁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}大家一起來玩心跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}別做多餘的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}呃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好 那我就這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我要這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒有惡意反而更讓人害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}1 2
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}自食惡果了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你拉住那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}終於感覺要洗完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這些就是最後的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}污漬都洗掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}紐扣也掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}肯 肯定是開線了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:10:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不過玩偶倒是洗的超完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}眼睛！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就趁這個機會把制服翻新一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}翻新
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那麼 迷你裙式的和服怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}必須是帶花邊的連衣圍裙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}迷你裙 花邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我覺得玩偶裝挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}像提比那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}夏天估計會很熱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}也有夏季樣式的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這根本不是衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不過這制服還是挺讓人不捨的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這個我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}現在我要是不穿沒兔耳朵的工作服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就會感覺很不自在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這是被洗腦了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}學姐穿Fleur的制服很搭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}甘兔的制服也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}之前提出來的方案
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就把它們輪流著用上怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.24,0:11:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}理世也想玩玩提比的cosplay嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那樣好像也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.41,0:11:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 不 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好壯觀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}可別被風給吹走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}剛說完 手帕就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.13,0:11:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我抓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}現在我感受到了紗路家的胖次被吹走的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}才沒那麼容易被吹走的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.81,0:11:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這制服是從哪裡買來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是我媽媽做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.03,0:11:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}親手做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}手好巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}說等我長大了 能和朋友一起穿上它工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}給我做了三種顏色的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}還有黃色和綠色的未成品 真是令人煩惱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是想讓你把好多朋友都叫來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}千夜和紗路也一定很合身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}千夜有甘兔 紗路還有Fleur的工作要忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但是要把這麼有愛的衣服翻新什麼的 怎能如此輕易的說出口！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.82,0:12:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哼哼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}等下 開線的部分我要全都修好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好了 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}學 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:13:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}今天工作結束後請改回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}什麼都別說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}非常的pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.11,0:13:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}晚飯做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}今天是什麼便宜來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}秋刀魚應該是特價
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}秋刀魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛應該再多吃點魚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}做咖哩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}有在聽我說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咖哩的話 就要克服平時不愛吃的蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}胡蘿蔔也要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我昨天吃了一口蘆筍來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}所以不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}所以說昨天已經吃了一口蘆筍…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不是這個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.15,0:13:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}跟姐姐說話不用敬語也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:14:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛跟誰都不說敬語呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我的座右銘可是見面3秒就能成爲朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真羡慕你這麼開朗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我周圍一直都是客人和長輩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.03,0:14:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}改不過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這樣啊 那來練習一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}練習？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃 心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}兩個人去買東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}來 智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是 千…夜 紗…路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:37.79,ZS,,0,0,0,,註：這裡さん說了一半硬改成ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你…好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你是憋著想去廁所嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}最重要的是要像智乃自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不要勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對對 別勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}輪到讓她這麼做的你來說？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:15:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}紗路也是 在理世面前很生硬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}瞎 瞎操心 人家是學姐嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}變柔和的秘訣就是一直保持笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}來笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真以為陪笑比得過我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}明明只是陪笑卻無比耀眼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}紗路你要做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咖哩吧…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那要不要大家一起做一起吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Nice idea！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對 爸爸 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我們要在紗路家吃完飯再回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}買了好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}明明這個月手頭也很緊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不過理世學姐會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}紗路 也邀請一下理世怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:16:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 是 是呢 既然千夜這麼說我就打電話問問好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}喂喂？ 紗路？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個 學姐 大家說要一起開咖哩派對…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}在理世面前很生硬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}紗路？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}馬上來我家YO！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}YO！？難道說現在很流行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.43,0:16:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊啊 這就去YO！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:33.13,Default,,500,0,0,,{\be3}答應了嗎 YO YO YO！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.02,0:16:33.75,Default,,0,500,0,,{\be3}已經走偏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}秘方是要加些蜂蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}最後是這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}看起來很昂貴的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是我老爸的部下帶來的伴手禮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但是他不太喜歡甜食 就讓我分給大家吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哇 我要吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}往這裡面加一塊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}在咖哩裡加巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:16:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}味道會更濃郁的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嘿～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不愧是學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}剩下的就是像這樣再煮一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}臉好紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是加了白蘭地的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真是的 成何體統！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這樣也算是我的妹妹嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}居然吃個酒芯巧克力都會醉！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.24,0:17:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}輪不到會醉咖啡因的人來說吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這可不能把玫瑰念珠交給你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}吃了高級食品連性格都變成大小姐了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}感覺夢到自己進了紗路的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我的學校在你眼裡就是這印象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦 智乃呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你突然發火把她嚇跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對不起 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我會做個乖孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}別生我的氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}什麼情況！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛的努力終於有回報了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真是日思夜盼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}來這邊 快來 過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}千夜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不挑人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}理世姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我會幫忙做飯的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}罕見！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 那能幫我處理剩下的胡蘿蔔嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}雖然我不想引戰 但事已至此別無他法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}賭上姐姐之名一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不好意思 這次我可不會拱手相讓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}紗路姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這孩子酒醒之後一定會羞死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}在Rabbit House裡這都是家常便飯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}實力決定一切？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}野雁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你也來湊熱鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要胡蘿蔔嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不行 不是說好食物由自己解決的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這兩人還是有點隔閡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}慢慢來就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}目標 為兔子所愛的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心好累不想再愛了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你喜歡現在的我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對姐姐不必用敬語哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}莫非是很在意我說的話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對 不 起 智 乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對不起 智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我最喜歡往常那樣的智乃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個…我並沒喝醉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哦 愛的力量讓你恢復正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}之…之前的都是演技啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.81,0:20:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}難為情？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.43,0:20:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是能記得酒醉時候的事的類型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}都是演技啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哇 我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.33,0:20:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這是家常菜「部隊咖哩」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}喂 胡蘿蔔也要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}媽媽 睜一隻眼閉一隻眼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}姐姐說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不要在這種時候裝出一副好姐妹的樣子！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}吃得真飽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}大家一起吃飯果然更香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}剩下的我都分好了 留著以後吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}學姐 這夠我吃一輩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.43,0:21:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}看來現在這種關係更輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}巧克力也吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}紗路吃得最多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我聽說巧克力也含有咖啡因…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.58,0:21:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不要你們今天就這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}回去！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃剛完紗路又來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我更喜歡這樣的紗路哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 放開我
Comment: 0,0:00:00.14,0:00:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}ED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.98,0:23:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}洗衣機報廢的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}最近的機器真不禁用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.95,0:23:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}進去了吧？
